    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Genjutsu </p><p>Prerequisite: Psychosis Adept, Level 8+ </p><p>You've become adept at causing unmatched psychotic trauma to others minds.</p><p> You gain the following benefits: </p><p>• The Pain genjutsu no longer ends when its effect is first applied.</p><p> • The Doubled Pain genjutsu increases its damage die by 1 step.</p><p> • The Unlimited Pain genjutsu no longer needs a direct line of sight, instead so long as you know the target creatures name, they can hear you, and they are within range, they suffer its effects as normal.</p><p></p>",
